# {{projectName}}

An X Space voice agent powered by [xspace-agent](https://github.com/xspace-agent/xspace-agent).

## Setup

1. Fill in your API keys in `.env`
2. Run the agent:

```bash
npm start -- https://x.com/i/spaces/YOUR_SPACE_ID
```

## Configuration

Edit `.env` to configure:

- `AI_PROVIDER` — AI provider (`{{provider}}`)
- `{{providerEnvKey}}` — Your API key
- `X_AUTH_TOKEN` — Your X authentication token
- `TTS_PROVIDER` — Text-to-speech provider (`openai` or `elevenlabs`)
